<p>Suppose we have a model $y \sim \beta_{0} + \beta_{1} x_{1} + \beta_{2} x_{2}$, more specifically, let</p>

<p>\begin{equation}
\beta_{0} = 3, \quad \beta_{1} = \beta_{2} = 1.
\end{equation}</p>

<p>and let the sample contain 100 elements</p>

